<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.2">
<l>aṅkuṟṟē ṉallē ṉiṅkuṟṟē ṉallē ṉuṉṉaik kāṇumavāvil vīḻntunāṉ</l>
<l>eṅkuṟ ṟēṉumal lēṉilaṅkaiceṟṟa vammāṉē</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷ cērmaṇi māṭa nīṭu cirīvara maṅkala nakaruṟai</l>
<l>caṅku cakkarat tāy.tami yēṉuk karuḷāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I don’t exist there, I don’t exist here; sunk in the desire to see you I</l>
<l>exist nowhere, o lord who subdued Laṅka.</l>
<l>O you with the conch [and] discus who stays in the city of Cirīvaramaṅkalam</l>
<l>tall with jeweled mansions joined by the moom, be gracious to me who is alone.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
